title: Avaya 45xx: Temperature
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/avaya
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the temperature of Avaya 45xx devices.

 You can configure upper levels for {WARN}/{CRIT} (default 55, 60).

 The service goes {WARN}/{CRIT} if the temperature exceeds these levels.

 The check uses the S5-CHASSIS-MIB.

item:
 The index of the temperature sensor.

discovery:
 One service is created for each temperature sensor.
